- cs.GR (Graphics) is also likely as the paper mentions the use of video and telemetry data, which may involve graphics processing.
- cs.SD (Sound) is less likely but still possible as the paper mentions collecting environmental data, which may include sound.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also possible as the paper deals with collecting and synchronizing various types of data, including video and telemetry.
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is less likely but still possible as the paper may have implications for the social and ethical aspects of eSports training and data analysis.
